[21:52:29.523] [INFO ]   Q: How does NovaAI's performance review cycle work?
[21:52:29.523] [INFO ] ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
