[03:48:59.309] [INFO ] ── RAW ANSWER ──
[03:48:59.309] [INFO ]     Here are the expense limits and submission requirements for hotel stays at NovaAI:
    
    **Hotel Stay Limits:**
    - Maximum nightly rate: **$250 USD** (excluding taxes and fees)
    - For stays in high-cost cities (e.g., New York, San Francisco, London), the limit is **$350 USD** per night
    - All bookings should be made in standard business-class accommodations
    
    **Submission Requirements:**
    - Expenses must be submitted within **30 days** of the stay
    - Use the **NovaAI Expense Portal** (Concur system)
    - Required documentation:
      - Itemized hotel receipt showing zero balance
      - Proof of payment (credit card statement page)
      - Business purpose must be included in the expense description
    
    **Additional Policy Notes:**
    - Incidental expenses (mini-bar, movies) are not reimbursable
    - Early departure fees are reimbursable with manager approval
    - All international stays require pre-approval from your department head
    
    Please refer to the **NovaAI Travel & Expense Policy (v3.1, updated March 2023)** for complete details. Contact Finance/AP if you need policy exceptions or have submission questions.
